  "detailed_description": "<h1>My new game</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>A nostalgia-infused pixel clicker in a comedy wrapper. <br>You play the part of a colonist set out to conquer new planets. As a supernova explosion takes out your ship's energy reserves, your only hope of getting back on course is a jerry-rigged old dynamo. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/699180/extras/1bc2ad0d318c63bc2487c4a20093ff6d.poster.avif?t=1769119981\" width=608 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/699180/extras/1bc2ad0d318c63bc2487c4a20093ff6d.webm?t=1769119981\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/699180/extras/1bc2ad0d318c63bc2487c4a20093ff6d.mp4?t=1769119981\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The game has: <br>* Stylish retro graphics <br>* A witty computer for a partner <br>* Ship improvements in all directions: a dynamo, a potato farm for energy generation and, of course, an antimatter distiller <br>* Smooth acceleration up to hyper-speed <br>* Space octopuses <br>And no lootboxes!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/699180/extras/a92b8572c8fe37bf9eba5a940832ffee.avif?t=1769119981\" width=616 height=108 /></span>",
